16	//! - [`framing`] : the stream-aware batch frame around opaque theory payloads.
17	//! - [`emit`] : an incremental ([`Sink`]-driven) emitter producing the same
18	//!   per-stream bytes as [`framing`] while the run is still in progress.
19	//! - [`errors`] : renderers for the runtime error lines emitted after parsing.
20	//! - [`stream`] : the two-stream output model ([`Stream`], [`Streams`]).
